import React from 'react'
import Footer from './Footer'

import {
    Button,
    Flex,
    Heading,
    Stack,
    Spacer,
    Text,
    Image,
    InputLeftElement,
    FormControl,
    Box,
    InputGroup,
    Icon,
    Grid,
    GridItem,
    FormLabel,
    Progress,
    Input,
    Textarea
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Checkbox, CheckboxGroup } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { HamburgerIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons'

const Session5 = () => {
    return (
        <Flex  minHeight="100vh" fontFamily="Roboto"  bg="#F9F9F9" direction="column"  align="center">
                <Flex width="90%" direction="row" justify="flex-start">
                    <HamburgerIcon w="30px" height="30px" mt="10px" />
                </Flex>
                <Flex  direction="column" justify="center" w="80%" align="center">
                <Box>
                    <Heading fontWeight="700" color="#141414" lineHeight="31px" fontSize="24px" textAlign="center">
                    Great session! Add participants and grow your community
                    </Heading>
                </Box>
           
            <Footer/>
            <Box w="137px" mt="50px"  mb="9px" height="5px" bg="black" borderRadius="100px"></Box>


                </Flex>
        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Session5
